{"tid":1794241,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"龍門老闆擺32圍 與抗爭者團圓","createTime":"2019-12-23T03:35:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T04:51:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"201308faccd100e36d63d4b925e73887383a0c79","tid":1794241,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T03:35:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191223/NJNVQGWLM3FP7E4UX5J5STBNQA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191223%2FNJNVQGWLM3FP7E4UX5J5STBNQA%2F&d=HJ1jiXHXfxJ2%2FxolOfbUwWhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=069a2c75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191223%2FNJNVQGWLM3FP7E4UX5J5STBNQA%2F&h=0f9e4424\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191223/NJNVQGWLM3FP7E4UX5J5STBNQA/</a><br />\n<br />\n龍門老闆擺32圍 與抗爭者團圓<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191223/large/1577031159_0da7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191223%2Flarge%2F1577031159_0da7.gif&h=68410ee3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n龍門老闆張俊傑昨與抗爭者齊齊食乳豬。黎樹雄攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】經典電影《龍門客棧》裏的龍門客棧是寒氣迫人的錦衣衞秘密基地，現實裏的龍門冰室是雪中送炭的義士喘息小窩。昨晚家家戶戶冬至慶團圓，有人卻因家庭政見分歧被趕出家門。「香港人嘅冰室資源中心」舉辦「香港兒女冬節晚宴」，慰勞為香港未來打拼的香港兒女。主辦者、龍門冰室老闆張俊傑盼這班兒女感受到人間有情，切勿失去對未來的希望。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「家長」預備聖誕禮物<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：千人撐維族 「再教育營遲早在港出現」<br />\n<br />\n這餐冬至飯與別不同，32圍圓桌上放置窩心曲奇，寄語在席者「安全回家」和「煲底見」，大批「家長」捐出厚禮，希望「子女」過個美滿聖誕，款待處擺放大量心意卡，讓難得安心飽腹的年輕人，看見同路人的支持，眾人開席先高叫「光復香港 時代革命」，再慢慢嘆蝦球、蟹鉗、南非鮑等佳餚，還有象徵團圓的湯丸。<br />\n<br />\n中心負責人「小總理」透露，黃藍政見撕裂不少家庭，本為人母的她常常在午夜後充當別人子女的樹窿，聆聽別人子女的心聲，有少年十多歲已缺乏家庭溫暖，與家人沒有交流，反送中運動爆發後更被拒之千里，需出外自行租屋。她慨嘆這些「仔女」需要的東西其實好簡單，不求家人凡事支持，只是希望得到點點諒解。<br />\n<br />\n有來吃冬至飯的「子女」說，自己以前是港豬不問世事，這場運動令她不斷進化和醒覺，但媽媽在她被捕後跟警察說「唔該你同佢講以後唔好再返屋企」，令她不敢想像被親母如此對待，求助無門之際，她遇上願意伸出援手的家長，一切令她感激不已。有70後「家長」則指，沒想過現時的年輕人要為生活躊躇，自己同一年紀時只知錢花在自己身上，他寄語大家路難行更要團結走下去。<br />\n<br />\n「無論你過去係點，都唔應該影響你去搵自己嘅未來」。龍門老闆張俊傑希望每一個年輕人都可以追尋自己的夢想，今日受助的人，他朝也回饋社會，一群有良心的人站出來為社會做多些事，建立真正的香港人精神，讓社會重拾希望。<br />\n<br />\n■記者袁楚雙<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191223/large/1577031158_1f40.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191223%2Flarge%2F1577031158_1f40.gif&h=42acd5bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有大批「家長」向抗爭者捐出禮物。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c046f3b3d555bd9812bc108499ecde287d771f","tid":1794241,"uid":114487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T03:36:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VgwZ4tD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVgwZ4tD.jpg&h=52b479a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TGepv8D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTGepv8D.jpg&h=265d7544&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ocgLfAm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FocgLfAm.jpg&h=e2a8e121&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"643979297bcc843a488b74cc2176bba17ed4cef0","tid":1794241,"uid":10290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T03:36:37.000Z","msg":"好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12375f12ecc25405f44b602f207a4d19270f1b6c","tid":1794241,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T03:36:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"